@startuml
!theme plain
title Epic 24 - US97: Grandpa Ciccio Boss (Cucù)

class GrandpaCiccioBoss {
    - loot_item : ItemString = "Ace"
    + start_cucu_challenge()
    + check_game_result(winner)
    + surrender_loot()
}

class CucuGame {
    - deck : List<Card>
    - player_card : Card
    - boss_card : Card
    + deal_cards()
    + player_attempts_swap() : bool
    + boss_turn_logic()
    + compare_cards() : Winner
    + get_final_winner() : Winner
}

class Player {
    + inventory : List<Item>
    + decide_keep_or_swap()
    + receive_item(item)
}

' Relazioni
GrandpaCiccioBoss ..> CucuGame : acts as Dealer
CucuGame --> Player : interacts with
GrandpaCiccioBoss --> Player : gives Ace on Win

note right of GrandpaCiccioBoss::surrender_loot
  Viene chiamato se il giocatore
  vince la partita a Cucù
end note

@enduml